# Important Files

- `.cursor/rules/important-files.mdc`: Lists all important files for the project
- `package.json`: NPM package configuration with scripts and dependencies
- `tsconfig.json`: TypeScript configuration
- `src/main.ts`: Main entry point for the MCP server
- `src/github-functions/base.ts`: Base GitHub functionality including Octokit initialization
- `src/github-functions/issues.ts`: GitHub API functions for issues
- `src/github-functions/pull-requests.ts`: GitHub API functions for pull requests
- `src/github-functions/index.ts`: Export file for GitHub functions
- `src/tools/issues.ts`: MCP server tools for GitHub issues
- `src/tools/pull-requests.ts`: MCP server tools for GitHub pull requests
- `src/tools/index.ts`: Export file for MCP tools
- `.env`: Environment variables for GitHub authentication (not committed to git)
- `.gitignore`: Specifies intentionally untracked files to ignore

Note: When adding new important files to the project, please add them to this list.